</head><body><table border=0 align=center width=80%><tr><td class=textbody><center><h1>Plane of Sky Quests</h1><br>by Korteal</center><br>To initiate all of these quests, you must speak to Wizard Schrock. He will ask if you wish to speak to Neasin or Abec. Asking for either quest giver, Schrock will hand you a book that you can read and then hand back. Once you hand Schrock back the book, the appropriate quest giver, Neasin or Abec, will appear.
<HR>
<b>You say, 'hail, Neasin Leornic!'</b>
<HR>
<b>You say, 'Concentration'</b>
<HR>
Neasin Leornic says ' Concentration it is. Proceed upward through the sky and return to me an Azure Tessera, an Augmentor's Gem, and a Grey Cloak. This will prove your ability to concentrate and I will reward you with an Augmentors Cloak.
<HR>
Azure Tessera (droppable): Found on island one in Sky from the Thunder Spirits (they all drop various Tessera for different classes) <BR>
Augmentor's Gem (droppable): A rare drop from the Protector of Sky on the Azarack Island in Sky. <BR>
Grey Damask Cloak (NO DROP): Found upon the Gorgalosk (the named gorgalosk inside the building on the 3rd island). 
<HR>
Augmentor's Mask <BR>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <BR>
AC: +6 Agi: +8 Dex: +4 Int: +9 Mana: +9 <BR>
Weight: 0.5 <BR>
Classes: Wizard <BR>
Races: All Races <BR>
Inventory Slot: Face
<HR>
<b>You say, 'Focus'</b>
<HR>
Neasin Leornic says 'Focus is a must. Travel among the residents of the sky and bring to me an Iron Disk, an Ethereal Opal, and a Woven Skull Cap. This will prove your ability to focus and I will reward you with Al`Kabors Cap.
<HR>
Iron Disk: (Droppable) Found upon Azarack's upon Azarack Isle. <BR>
Ethereal Opal: (Droppable) Found upon Watchful Guards or the Avenging Gazer on Gorgolosk Isle. <BR>
Woven Skull Cap: (No Drop) Found as a rare drop upon the Keeper of Souls. 
<HR>
Al'Kabor's Cap of Binding <BR>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <BR>
Charges: 4 <BR>
AC: +6 Str: +5 Int: +8 Fire Resist: +10 Cold Resist: +10 HP: +40 Mana: +20 <BR>
Weight: 0.2 <BR>
Classes: Wizard <BR>
Races: All Races <BR>
Inventory Slot: Head <BR>
Effect: Bonds of Force
<HR>
<b>You say, 'Meditation'</b>
<HR>
Neasin Leornic says 'A wizard is nothing without meditation. Meditation allows us to focus and concentrate when casting our spells of power. Fly to those above and return to me a Hyaline Globe, a Sky Topaz, and a High Quality Raiment. If you are successful, I will reward you with the Raiment of Thunder.
<HR>
Hyaline Globe: Found upon random mobs upon the third island. <BR>
Sky Topaz: Found on Soul Carriers and Essence Harvesters on the fourth island. <BR>
High Quality Raiment: Rare drop off of the Spiroc lord
<HR>
Raiment of Thunder <BR>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <BR>
Charges: 2 <BR>
AC: +4 Str: +5 Int: +5 Poison Resist: +10 Disease Resist: +5 Mana: +15 <BR>
Weight: 0.3 <BR>
Classes: Wizard <BR>
Races: All Races <BR>
Inventory Slot: Shoulder <BR>
Effect: Thunder Strike
<HR>
<b>You say, 'hail, Abec Ianor!"</b>
<HR>
<b>You say, 'Conception'</b>
<HR>
Abec Ianor says 'Conception is vital. Travel beyond and bring forth an Efreeti Statuette, a Mithril Air Ring, and a Box of Winds. From these I will produce a ring that will protect you wherever you go.
<HR>
Efreeti Statuette: DROPPABLE LORE ITEM. Drops off of Soul Carriers or Essence Harvesters on the 4th isle. <BR>
Mithril Air Ring: DROPPABLE. Found upon Spiroco Guardians as a rare drop upon the sixth isle. <BR>
Box of Winds: NO DROP. Found upon a Bzazzt Zazzt from the bee isle.
<HR>
Solidate Mithril Ring <BR>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <BR>
Charges: 3 <BR>
AC: +4 Str: +5 Agi: +6 Int: +5 Mana: +50 <BR>
Weight: 0.1 <BR>
Classes: Wizard <BR>
Races: All Races <BR>
Inventory Slot: Finger <BR>
Effect: Steelskin 
<HR>
<b>You say, 'Preparation'</b>
<HR>
Abec Ianor says 'Always be prepared. Adventure and return an Efreeti War Staff, some Lush Nectar, a Copper Air Band, and a large Sky Sapphire. And you shall be rewarded with the Staff of Storms. 
<HR>
Efreeti War Staff: Droppable. Found upon the Efreeti Noble Dojorn. Both Dojorn and the Overseer drop the staff <BR>
Lush Nectar: Droppable. Found upon Bzzazzt upon the bee isle. <BR>
Copper Air Band: Droppable. Found upon Fatestealer Drakes on the Sister of the Spire Isle. <BR>
Large Sky Sapphire: no drop. Found upon an Eye of Veeshan upon the last isle.
<HR>
Nargon's Staff <BR>
MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <BR>
Damage: 16 <BR>
Delay: 48 <BR>
Ratio: 3 Good <BR>
Int: +15 Magic Resist: +10 Disease Resist: +25 Mana: +75 <BR>
Weight: 4.0 <BR>
Weapon Skill: Two Hand Blunt <BR>
Classes: Wizard <BR>
Races: All Races <BR>
Inventory Slot: Primary
<HR>
<b>You say, 'Visualization'</b>
<HR>
Abec Ianor says 'Visualize and succeed. Proceed upward and bring to me a White-Tipped Spiroc Feather, a Pulsating Sapphire, and an Amethyst Amulet. With these items, I will be able to produce an amulet that will aid in your travels to our home.
<HR>
White-Tipped Spiroc Feather: Droppable. Found upon the Spiroc Isle (island #5) upon non-named spirocs. <BR>
Pulsating Sapphire: Droppable. Found upon Bzzazzts on the bee isle. <BR>
Amethyst Amulet: No Drop. Found upon the 'Sister of The Spire' on 7th island (drake island). This is the island's boss mob. 
<HR>
Amulet of Planar Transference <BR>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP <BR>
Charges: 1 <BR>
AC: +2 Agi: +5 Dex: +5 Cha: +2 Mana: +50 <BR>
Weight: 0.1 <BR>
Classes: Wizard <BR>
Races: All Races <BR>
Inventory Slot: Neck <BR>
Effect: Alter Plane: Sky</td></tr></table></body></html>